This week, we also focused on water, both during the journey and on Mars. We thought about recycling water similar to the ISS, but we can not recycle all water. Each cycle, we lose 5% of water. We also need to build a water system to filter the water. Another idea is that we could retrieve water from the frozen ice on the south pole. Although it could be a source of water, it is temporary because it would eventually run out.

